{"tid":1949404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯：贏唔到俄羅斯世界盃　就退出國家隊","createTime":"2020-03-29T15:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T07:10:38.000Z","uid":173952,"like":49,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"36eb92062df6d9864c4949a36a0526a58518349a","tid":1949404,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"因此美斯有感而發：「國家隊嘅成功，只取決於結果。如果呢次都贏唔到世界盃，唔會再有下次機會。如果再贏唔到，我得一條路揀，就係退出國家隊。我好想喺俄羅斯奪得冠軍，好想好似喺2014年咁，力拚到最後。」<span style=\"color: red;\">美斯於16年美洲國家盃決賽不敵智利後，曾一度退出國家隊，但於各個單位力挽底下，佢決定復出</span>，並於今次世界盃外圍賽，成為阿根廷晉身決賽嘅英雄。 <br />\n<br />\n其實佢退役左國家隊幾多次?"},{"pid":"df770abb89adfe2dd58923d7ca11e164c5acf7aa","tid":1949404,"uid":7043,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:17:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾小花淨係識哭哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ade6cc8c98c996e791e85b10812c3635b1e23d3","tid":1949404,"uid":79351,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:21:59.000Z","msg":"今年唔中武漢肺炎就當贏啦好無？"},{"pid":"b4f43bb4b9ffc6aaccf56d867db5fe6c6024fd7a","tid":1949404,"uid":173952,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:25:29.000Z","msg":"仲踢緊，即係贏左世界盃了"},{"pid":"78c0e043918140d45ce140bafec37c8447bc107a","tid":1949404,"uid":124439,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"真係有D悲情,自己一條友嬴到全世界個人榮譽但國家隊無次成功"},{"pid":"afe62695c7934fcb5951ec4cf4929f6d987ebc52","tid":1949404,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:26:29.000Z","msg":"足球唔係踢一個人<br />\n可以退定都得"},{"pid":"5208121c72a586fb4120c29dc6f2da1b0f41b2ef","tid":1949404,"uid":205403,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"都係領隊問題  唔識揀隊友"},{"pid":"86cf2def32b0eac66a696dce85661b722ebe4e16","tid":1949404,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:47:50.